{"tid":2289493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰王「親民」搭地鐵…腳邊大臣跪趴一地　貴妃復寵與皇后暗中較勁","createTime":"2020-11-17T09:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T10:53:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e528e13a27d53653c73afb86e8862deadf685266","tid":2289493,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5275/d5275158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5275%2Fd5275158.jpg&h=857e113d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5275/d5275162.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5275%2Fd5275162.jpg&h=2d333130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5275/d5275163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5275%2Fd5275163.jpg&h=e19931ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5275/d5275165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5275%2Fd5275165.jpg&h=27f63829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5275/d5275164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5275%2Fd5275164.jpg&h=eb5c38b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰王瓦吉拉隆功（Maha Vajiralongkorn）因在德國躲避新冠疫情，加上國內反王室的抗<br />\n議不斷，導致其聲譽一落千丈，近來頻頻在螢光幕前展現親民的一面，希望能挽回形象。<br />\n瓦吉拉隆功日前就帶著皇后蘇堤達一起參加新地鐵站的落成儀式，儘管想打親民牌，但還<br />\n是跟跪趴了一地的大臣形成強烈對比。另外剛復寵的貴妃也單獨出席活動，和皇后較勁意<br />\n味十足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201117/1856321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201117%2F1856321.htm&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM452AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=33c86dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201117/1856321.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f03152d50c88f52b42ccf669d25ffc8b31376cd","ti